      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and delivers a linear power band culminating at an 8,000 RPM redline. This unit features a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS system calibration and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring chassis rigidity under lateral load. With refreshed bushings and a precise steering rack, this chassis maintains its signature 50/50 weight distribution and communicative handling. A true driver\u2019s car for those who value analog performance and engineering integrity.",
